                            Arsitektur Modular & Ringan
                        </li>
                        <li data-target="sol-1" class="cursor-pointer border-2 border-black p-3 font-bold flex gap-3 items-center hover:bg-[#adff2f] transition-all">
                            <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-black text-white text-xs flex items-center justify-center">02</span>
                            Validasi Transaksi Real-time
                        </li>
                        <li data-target="sol-2" class="cursor-pointer border-2 border-black p-3 font-bold flex gap-3 items-center hover:bg-[#adff2f] transition-all">
                            <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-black text-white text-xs flex items-center justify-center">03</span>
